#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This addon reverts the behaviour of NVDA+f9 and NVDA+f10 that was introduced "
"in NVDA 2016.3."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dodatak vraća naredbe NVDA+F9 i NVDA+F10 na one naredbe, koje su "
"predstavljene u NVDA verziji 2016.3."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The old behaviour copies the selection to the clipboard on the first press "
"of NVDA+f10, while the new one selects on the first press and copies on the "
"second.  The new behaviour has some disadvantages. Text can't be copied "
"without being selected (and thus moving the cursor), where that's available. "
"For places it's not (example the console), it adds an extra press of "
"NVDA+f10."
msgstr ""
"Stare naredbe kopiraju sadržaj kad se tipke NVDA+F10 pritisnu jednom. Nove "
"naredbe odabiru tekst pri prvom pritisku, a kopiraju pri dvostrukom "
"pritisku. Nove naredbe imaju određene mane. Tekst se ne može kopirati prije "
"nego što se odabere (zbog čega se pokazivač pomiče), tamo gdje je to "
"dostupno. Tamo gdje nije (na primjer u konzoli), dodaje jedan pritisak tipki "
"NVDA+F10."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The addon adds two new gestures under the Classic Selection category to "
"start and end selection, which are bound to NVDA+f9 and NVDA+f10 by default."
msgstr ""
"Dodatak dodaje dvije nove naredbe u kategoriju „Klasični odabir” za početak "
"i kraj odabira, koje su standardno postavljene na NVDA+F9 i NVDA+F10."

